# 🛒 E-Commerce Sales Analytics System

## 📌 Project Overview
This project is a complete E-Commerce Sales Analytics Dashboard developed using SQL and Power BI. The project focuses on analyzing sales performance, customer behavior, product profitability, and regional trends to generate actionable business insights.

The dashboard helps businesses monitor KPIs, identify top-performing products, analyze customer segments, and improve decision-making.

---

# 🚀 Tools & Technologies Used

- SQL
- Power BI
- Excel / CSV Dataset
- GitHub

---

# 📊 Dashboard Features

## Executive Overview
- Total Sales
- Total Profit
- Total Orders
- Profit Margin

## Sales Analysis
- Monthly Sales Trend
- State Wise Sales
- Category Wise Revenue
- Profit by Month

## Customer Analysis
- Top Customers
- Customer Segmentation
- Payment Mode Analysis

## Product Analysis
- Top Selling Products
- Product Profitability
- Quantity Analysis

---

# 🧠 SQL Concepts Used

- JOINS
- GROUP BY
- ORDER BY
- Aggregate Functions
- Window Functions
- CTE (Common Table Expressions)
- Subqueries

---

# 📈 KPIs

| KPI | Description |
|---|---|
| Total Sales | Overall revenue generated |
| Total Profit | Overall profit earned |
| Total Orders | Number of orders placed |
| Profit Margin | Profit percentage from sales |

